    <item>
      <title>特朗普寻求年轻人投票，试图将 TikTok 法案归咎于拜登</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/tiktok-ban-trump-tries-to-blame-biden-for-divest-or-ban-bill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普试图指责总统乔·拜登制定了强制出售社交媒体平台 TikTok 的立法，尽管他在任期间曾试图亲自禁止该公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/tiktok-ban-trump-tries-to-blame-biden-for-divest-or-ban-bill</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 20:08:37 GMT</pubDate>
