      <title>特朗普在最高法院的豁免策略：拖延仍然是胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/trump-s-immunity-case-at-supreme-court-a-delay-means-a-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最高法院对唐纳德·特朗普声称因试图推翻 2020 年选举而获得刑事指控豁免的历史性考虑遇到了严峻的现实：日历与宪法一样重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/trump-s-immunity-case-at-supreme-court-a-delay-means-a-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
